{"title":"Far Metformina-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Far Metformina-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Metformina","guid":"NQd-S3eljjWOosPAqWE5kQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"• Primera línea: Recomendada para casi todos los pacientes con DM2, especialmente con sobrepeso/obesidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"2","parent":"0","text":"• Familia: Biguanidas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"• Acciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• No provoca hipoglicemias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• Disminuye insulino resistencia (insulino sensibilizador).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"• Reduce glucosa sanguínea (↓ gluconeogénesis, ↓ glucogenólisis en hígado).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"3","text":"• Aumenta receptores de insulina en adipocitos y células musculares.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"3","text":"• Estimula transporte de glucosa y síntesis de glucógeno en músculo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"• Efectos\\NExtraglicémicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Mejora perfil lipídico (↓ TG, ↓ LDL, ↑ HDL).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• Disminuye inhibidor 1 del activador del plasminógeno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• Mejora anomalías fibrinolíticas (98).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"Eficacia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Monoterapia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• ↓ Glucosa plasmática en ayunas: 60-70 mg/dL.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• ↓ A1c: 1.5-2.0%.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• Formulaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Liberación simple/inmediata: 2 veces/día.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Liberación prolongada: 1-2 veces/día.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Dosis máxima: 2550 mg/día (dosis >2000 mg con escasa eficacia adicional y peor tolerancia).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\NSecundarios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Digestivos: Diarrea, meteorismo, dolor abdominal (frecuentes y dosis-dependientes).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Mejoran con el tiempo, reducción de dosis o cambio a liberación prolongada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• Administración: Post comidas para mejorar tolerancia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Precauciones y\\NContraindicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• VFG <30 mL/min: No usar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• VFG <45 mL/min: Reducir dosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Insuficiencia hepática moderada: No usar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"• Condiciones de riesgo: Seguimiento estrecho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"• Acidosis láctica: Complicación rara pero grave, en contextos de enfermedad grave, hipoxemia, hipoperfusión tisular o insuficiencia renal aguda.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"25","text":"• Suspensión:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• En enfermedad grave, vómitos, deshidratación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• 24h antes de cirugías o exámenes con medios de contraste.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"25","text":"• Vitamina B12: Monitorización periódica, suplementar si deficiente (especialmente en ancianos y vegetarianos).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Beneficios\\NCardiovasculares","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• UKPDS: Único medicamento que ↓ muerte relacionada con DM, infarto agudo al miocardio y accidente cerebrovascular (67).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• Prevención ECV: Sugerido en varios estudios, aunque no diseñados específicamente para este efecto (100).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"Características de la\\NMetformina (Tabla 5)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Eficacia: Alta.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Costo: Bajo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"• Seguridad: Alta (con las\\Nprecauciones adecuadas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Formulaciones\\Ny Dosis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"1. Metformina\\Nliberación simple","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Formulación (mg): 500, 850, 1000.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"• Dosis diaria (mg): 1500 - 2550.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"• No usar con VFG < 30 mL/min.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"2. Metformina\\Nliberación prolongada","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Formulación (mg): 500, 750, 1000.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Dosis diaria (mg): 1500 - 2550.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Reducir dosis con VFG < 45 mL/min.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"K4ysz3eftwKhkq98jk2tow","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Medicamento de primera línea: Tratar diabetes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• Suspensión: En caso de enfermedad grave, vómitos,\\Ndeshidratación, 24h antes de cirugías/exámenes con contraste.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"• Contraindicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• VFG <30 mL/min.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"51","text":"• Reducir dosis si VFG <45 mL/min.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"• Vitamina B12: Monitorización periódica recomendada.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":57,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Far Metformina-2024","id":"map_758","resolved_references":[]}